author: timesofindia.indiatimes.com
title: Rii spotted at Fuzz culture and Oh, Rocket gig
text:
Delhi, the swag capital, and Kolkata, the culture capital of the country, came together last Saturday to present indie music lovers with a memorable evening.Held at a five-star property's club lounge, the gig brought together bands Fuzz Culture and Oh, Rocket.
Delhi duo Arsh and Srijan of Fuzz Culture made the guests swoon to their electronica rock beats. They performed compositions like Animals, Do we get a Grammy, no, and Wolf in sheep's clothing. On the other hand, homegrown outfit Oh, Rocket performed numbers from their debut EP released last year -Cat door back door man and Mechanical kimono. Actress Rii, who is a regular to these city gigs, was spotted grooving to their music.
